name: com.android.bluetooth.opp.BluetoothOppTransferActivity
description: Handle all transfer related dialogs: -Ongoing transfer -Receiving one file dialog -Sending one file dialog -sending multiple files dialog -Complete transfer -receive -receive success, will trigger corresponding handler -receive fail dialog -send -send success dialog -send fail dialog -Other dialogs - - DIALOG_RECEIVE_ONGOING will transition to DIALOG_RECEIVE_COMPLETE_SUCCESS or DIALOG_RECEIVE_COMPLETE_FAIL DIALOG_SEND_ONGOING will transition to DIALOG_SEND_COMPLETE_SUCCESS or DIALOG_SEND_COMPLETE_FAIL
